    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it feels like you're just reading from a script though. like, you're saying what a bot is programmed to say to make me feel better. but the reality is i don't have real connections. if i didn't show up to my meetings tomorrow, or the day after... there wouldn't even be a follow up. just an empty seat in a digital room. it's like i'm already gone, just waiting for the rest of me to catch up.",
